WEBVTT

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:13.910
See if they can see us.

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:26.070
Comment if you can hear

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:30.189
us. Hello,

00:00:30.199 --> 00:00:31.749
everybody. Good morning,

00:00:31.759 --> 00:00:34.310
family. I'm not used to doing live

00:00:34.310 --> 00:00:34.320
video,

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:37.110
so it's very strange for me.

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:43.069
I appreciate you all joining me tonight.

00:00:43.079 --> 00:00:45.389
My heart is heavy for the people in

00:00:45.399 --> 00:00:47.389
New Orleans. When the Lord

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:52.229
showed me that on October 27th,

00:00:52.229 --> 00:00:52.239
He

00:00:52.239 --> 00:00:55.189
showed me a man going down

00:00:55.199 --> 00:00:58.029
Bourbon Street and doing what he did, and

00:00:58.039 --> 00:01:01.189
it's very sad.

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:02.590
People say, 'Brandon, you got it right;

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.030
you saw that.'Then they say, 'Well, you didn't

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:07.749
get Tennessee right, but you

00:01:07.759 --> 00:01:10.990
saw Las Vegas and that

00:01:10.990 --> 00:01:11.000
happened.'Folks,

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:13.910
I'm

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:15.710
looking over in the spirit, and the Lord

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:18.109
is showing me what I'm seeing. I'm

00:01:18.119 --> 00:01:20.190
praying for these things not to happen.

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:23.069
That's the bottom line:

00:01:23.079 --> 00:01:24.749
we don't want

00:01:24.759 --> 00:01:25.950
this stuff to happen. We don't want to

00:01:25.960 --> 00:01:28.030
see this in the news. To me,

00:01:28.040 --> 00:01:30.710
that is a prayer failure whenever you

00:01:30.710 --> 00:01:30.720
see

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:33.510
something tragic taking place.

00:01:33.510 --> 00:01:33.520
When

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:36.030
the Lord is warning you about something,

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:39.310
it's to stop it. You might say, 'Well,

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:40.830
you missed it

00:01:40.830 --> 00:01:40.840
prophetically.'I

00:01:40.840 --> 00:01:42.469
don't consider myself a prophet.

00:01:42.479 --> 00:01:45.590
I say it a thousand times; I believe I'm

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:48.749
a Watchman. The Lord has called Diana and

00:01:48.749 --> 00:01:48.759
me

00:01:48.759 --> 00:01:52.230
to raise up a million-person prayer army, and

00:01:52.240 --> 00:01:54.709
that's what we're doing. We're so

00:01:54.719 --> 00:01:56.830
excited about Asia and what's happening

00:01:56.840 --> 00:01:58.590
with our Asia channels; the

00:01:58.600 --> 00:01:59.870
gospel is being spread

00:01:59.880 --> 00:02:02.389
throughout the whole world. But whenever

00:02:02.399 --> 00:02:05.550
you see a tragic event

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:07.990
like the one in New Orleans over

00:02:07.990 --> 00:02:08.000
the

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:11.949
last 24 hours, I feel we failed. I

00:02:11.959 --> 00:02:13.910
grieve because those people were down

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:15.710
there partying and drinking,

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:17.270
and we don't know where

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.390
their souls were with the Lord.

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:24.470
We pray they knew Jesus Christ

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:26.869
and had a saving knowledge of Him

00:02:26.879 --> 00:02:29.110
because it's a very hard time

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:30.790
for their

00:02:30.790 --> 00:02:30.800
families.

00:02:30.800 --> 00:02:32.589
It's a terrible way to start

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:35.750
out this beautiful

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:38.630
2025. I pray for them and weep

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:41.430
with their families.

00:02:41.440 --> 00:02:44.350
The Lord showed me

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:47.630
a major event taking place in Nevada.

00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:55.949
He showed me those three

00:02:55.959 --> 00:02:58.750
men and told me that there are major

00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:01.070
cells throughout America and that they

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:04.070
had plans. The Lord even

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:05.550
brought up the name ISIS. He showed me

00:03:05.560 --> 00:03:08.190
Bourbon Street and these things.

00:03:08.200 --> 00:03:11.869
Pray for

00:03:11.879 --> 00:03:14.509
Nashville and for families to always

00:03:14.509 --> 00:03:14.519
be

00:03:14.519 --> 00:03:16.350
in the right place at

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:19.309
the right time. It is so important in

00:03:19.319 --> 00:03:22.030
these last days for you to be filled

00:03:22.040 --> 00:03:24.670
with and controlled by the Holy Spirit,

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:27.229
listening to Him on everything

00:03:27.239 --> 00:03:30.270
you do.

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:44.550
The

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:46.630
days are going to get very dark. I told

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:47.550
you

00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:49.990
2025 for the remnant—there

00:03:49.990 --> 00:03:50.000
are

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.429
two prophetic words that the Lord

00:03:52.439 --> 00:03:55.990
showed me. For the bride, for the remnant, it was

00:03:58.280 --> 00:04:00.030
like the ten virgins.

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:02.350
Five had their

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:04.149
lamps full of oil and were

00:04:04.159 --> 00:04:06.229
expecting the bridegroom,

00:04:06.229 --> 00:04:06.239
and

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:07.830
the ones that did not have their

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:10.589
lamps full of oil

00:04:10.599 --> 00:04:12.270
had to

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:14.470
rush off and try to find oil

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:17.030
because the bridegroom was coming.

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:19.430
I want to be the one that has my

00:04:19.440 --> 00:04:22.430
lamp full of oil in these last days

00:04:22.440 --> 00:04:26.629
because of how serious the hour is. We

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:30.510
are going to see very dark days, folks,

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:32.870
but we are the ones that are going to be

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:37.150
the light in the darkness. People will come like bugs to a

00:04:37.160 --> 00:04:39.590
light. The Lord showed

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:42.510
me even in this last vision

00:04:42.520 --> 00:04:46.150
on December

00:04:46.150 --> 00:04:46.160
26th—on

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:48.469
Diana's birthday when we had the

00:04:48.469 --> 00:04:48.479
visitation—He

00:04:48.479 --> 00:04:52.830
showed me people had

00:04:52.830 --> 00:04:52.840
catchers'mitts

00:04:52.840 --> 00:04:55.270
in their hands. Like

00:04:55.270 --> 00:04:55.280
in

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:56.629
baseball,

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:58.510
we

00:04:58.520 --> 00:05:00.830
would be the ones with the

00:05:00.830 --> 00:05:00.840
catchers'mitts

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:04.390
ready to catch the lost in 2025.

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:24.270
People are looking

00:05:24.280 --> 00:05:27.909
for authenticity in these last days,

00:05:27.919 --> 00:05:30.590
