00:05:54.520 --> 00:05:57.510
People are wanting a true

00:05:57.520 --> 00:06:00.270
and authentic move of God,

00:06:00.280 --> 00:06:04.309
and I believe God has

00:06:04.319 --> 00:06:07.430
